OL,3,CJeremy Clarkson launches helpline for
OL,4,Cfarmers struggling with mental health
OL,6,FJeremy Clarkson is teaming up with the
OL,7,Ffree text support service, Shout, to
OL,8,Fprovide around the clock help for
OL,9,Ffarmers who are facing mental health
OL,10,Fchallenges.
OL,12,FThanks to funding from Clarkson's beer
OL,13,Fbrand, Hawkstone, farmers who might be
OL,14,Fstruggling in silence can text the
OL,15,Fword 'Hawkstone' to 85258 at any time
OL,16,Fof day or night to start a
OL,17,Fconversation with a trained Shout
OL,18,FVolunteer.
