OL,3,CJeremy Clarkson launches helpline for
OL,4,Cfarmers struggling with mental health
OL,6,FThis dedicated keyword allows the
OL,7,Fvolunteer to quickly identify a farmer
OL,8,Fin need and provide tailored support.
OL,10,FFarming has been described as one of
OL,11,Fthe toughest jobs in the world,
OL,12,Fphysically demanding with long hours,
OL,13,Foften spent alone.
OL,15,FClarkson has helped to shine a light
OL,16,Fon how difficult it is to be a farmer
OL,17,Fon his Amazon Prime Video show,
OL,18,FClarkson's Farm.
