OL,3,CJeremy Clarkson launches helpline for
OL,4,Cfarmers struggling with mental health
OL,6,FThe Top Gear star said: "Farming can
OL,7,Fbe a struggle so if you are finding it
OL,8,Fa bit tough at the moment, text
OL,9,FHAWKSTONE to 85258 and you'll get free
OL,10,Fconfidential support from a very
OL,11,Fexperienced team of people.
OL,13,F"It could be worth sending a message,
OL,14,Fit's better than suffering in silence."
OL,16,FVirtually all UK farmers (95%) under
OL,17,Fthe age of 40 rank poor mental health
OL,18,Fas one of the biggest hidden problems
OL,19,Ffacing the industry (Farm Safety
OL,20,FFoundation, 2021).
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
