OL,3,CJeremy Clarkson launches helpline for
OL,4,Cfarmers struggling with mental health
OL,6,FThey face unique challenges,
OL,7,Fparticularly during demanding periods
OL,8,Flike harvest season.
OL,10,FCredit: Hawkstone
OL,12,FThe partnership is supported by farmer
OL,13,FKaleb Cooper who shot to fame after
OL,14,Fappearing on Clarkson's Farm.
OL,16,FHe said: "Farming is an incredibly
OL,17,Fhard job and there are statistics out
OL,18,Fthere to show that mental health
OL,19,Fchallenges in farming have risen in
OL,20,Frecent years.
