OL,3,CJeremy Clarkson launches helpline for
OL,4,Cfarmers struggling with mental health
OL,6,F"Some people don't like talking about
OL,7,Ftheir problems face-to-face or find it
OL,8,Fdifficult to open up to someone they
OL,9,Fknow, so we have teamed up with Shout
OL,10,Fto allow farmers to send a simple text
OL,11,Fand get the support they need."
OL,13,FSarah Kendrick, Clinical Director at
OL,14,FShout said: "Our aim is to help people
OL,15,Ffeel connected, and to find a place
OL,16,Fwhere they're able to think through
OL,17,Fwhat their problems are.
